N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4226.1 - Duties of starter

State Regulations
(a) The starter
shall give all orders necessary for securing a fair start. (b) He shall report to the judges, by whom
and by what cause any delay was occasioned and any cases of misconduct by
assistant starters or by jockeys when under his orders. Notes
